{"tid":259882,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"我走過山時，山不說話， 我路過海時，海不說話","createTime":"2017-05-27T09:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-22T07:47:07.000Z","uid":15854,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"660d20d8a923abb2fc56920021aec51ab00e89d2","tid":259882,"uid":15854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T09:55:34.000Z","msg":"我走過山時，山不說話，<br />\n我路過海時，海不說話，<br />\n小毛驢滴滴答答，倚天劍伴我走天涯。<br />\n大家都說我因為愛著楊過大俠， 才在峨嵋山出了家，<br />\n其實我只是愛上了峨嵋山上的雲和霞， 像極了十六歲那年的煙花。"},{"pid":"cd70462e66be755cc1170a28b289afa222eb01dd","tid":259882,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T09:57:02.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"61a0553da86aff7335ba63c822ece562133974f6","tid":259882,"uid":15854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T10:00:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好</blockquote><br />\n慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9725258fe22426c90ae6dfb478422b82db2ba73b","tid":259882,"uid":45817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T10:01:00.000Z","msg":"哩段真係好正"},{"pid":"17f717041f5c26f1100b908ecd33251b8c068ff3","tid":259882,"uid":61317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T07:47:07.000Z","msg":"唔係大陸啲人自己作架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}